sequenceDiagram
    actor Teacher
    participant API as FastAPI Backend
    participant HRAT as HRAT Engine
    participant NLP as NLP Analyzer (spaCy)
    participant ML as ML Model (RandomForest)
    participant SHAP as SHAP Explainer
    participant DB as Database

    note over Teacher,DB: Triggered at POST /screenings/session/complete

    Teacher->>API: {session_id, student_id, nlp_notes}

    API->>HRAT: finalize(session_id)
    HRAT-->>API: feature_vector [q1..q20 averaged scores]

    alt nlp_notes provided
        API->>NLP: analyze_observation_notes(nlp_notes)
        NLP->>NLP: tokenize + lemmatize (spaCy en_core_web_sm)
        NLP->>NLP: match lemmas against LD keyword sets
        NLP-->>API: {detected_indicators, keyword_matches, flag_counts}
    end

    API->>ML: predict_with_explanation(feature_vector)
    ML->>ML: load ml_model.joblib (MultiOutputClassifier)
    ML->>ML: predict probabilities for 5 LD labels

    ML->>SHAP: TreeExplainer.shap_values(feature_vector)
    SHAP->>SHAP: compute per-feature SHAP contributions
    SHAP->>SHAP: rank top 3 features per LD
    SHAP-->>ML: shap_values + top_features per LD

    ML->>ML: generate_narrative(student_name, ld, probability, top_features)
    ML-->>API: {ld_scores, shap_top_features, narrative_text}

    API->>DB: INSERT Screening(student_id, assessor_id, answers, nlp_notes)
    DB-->>API: screening_id

    API->>DB: INSERT PredictionResult(screening_id, dyslexia_score, dyscalculia_score, dysgraphia_score, nvld_score, apd_score)

    API->>HRAT: delete_session(session_id)

    API-->>Teacher: {screening_id, predictions: {ld: score}, nlp_flags, explanations, narrative}
